&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5. Managing models and forecasting&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;build appropriate transport models capable of providing forecasts and input to operational, environmental and economic appraisal of transport solutions.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;P2: Delivering to agreed timescales, costs and quality standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;P4: Adhering to employer policies and procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;P9: Informing and enabling decision making&lt;/li&gt;
